# Phase 4 Rules — Workspace and Reporting

## What This Phase Builds

- Diagnostic hub and drilldown pages (UI for scorecards, findings, contradictions, impacts)
- Study & Snapshot Service: saved queries, frozen snapshots, comparison boards, annotations, evidence bundles
- Report template system and rendering pipeline (PDF, HTML, PPTX)
- 7 standard report templates (Full Assessment, Executive Summary, Vacancy Deep Dive, Leasing Deep Dive, Competitive Analysis, Progress Tracking, Door Opener)
- Custom report creation from any combination of section types
- Export formats for evidence bundles and rendered reports
- Analysis Lab: guided pivots, SQL access, drilldowns, compare views
- First consultant pilot on live engagements

## Prerequisites

Phase 3 must be complete: full diagnostic pipeline operational (metrics computed, scorecards scored, findings compiled, impacts estimated, contradictions detected).

